<br>
It would almost be like open seminars on class tactics, etc. Any big brother could also do guild recruiting while they were there as well. <br>
<br>
This might be better as a bi-weekly thing, but that would depend on how many volunteers we have. The web site is a good idea and normally I'd volunteer my services, however I'm about at the maximum web work I can do. :-) Any other webmasters out there wish to volunteer some time to this? <br>
<br>
Haemish MacLennan<br>
