<br>
I still like the one newbie to one big brother though, so both parties can get some friendships going, which is really important.<br>
<br>
As for the webpage, I can make one, only part I would need some help with would be the submission area, my knowledge of making forms has declined a good bit heh.<br>
<br>
<br>
Also, on the problem of actually getting newbies, we could use the Submit Press Release form on the Council page to advertise the site, and maybe have an initial event like the one Haemish suggested to introduce newbies to the concept and maybe get some recruits.<br>
<br>
Oh, and ill obviously volunteer to be one of the mage tutors, Id love to show some newbie Magicians how much thier class really does rule =)<br>
